## Failure modes

| Mode | Detection | Handling |
|---|---|---|
| Auth expired | 401 from MCP | Refresh token; surface to operator if refresh fails |
| Rate limit hit | 429 from MCP | Retry-after honor; queue retries |
| MCP server crashed | Tool call hangs | Restart server; log to audit trail |

